sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.soql

Class SOQLEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.soql.MapScriptObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScriptObject

    public class SOQLEngine
extends JSJavaScriptEngine
    This is SOQL (Simple Object Query Language) engine. This uses JavaScript engine for the "select" and "where" expression parts.
